{"tid":1297610,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[警惕] 警犬呢兩日無數嘅PR同小動作係為日後濫權升級鋪路","createTime":"2019-07-08T16:09:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T16:27:15.000Z","uid":168267,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e058dd75f759d82a2bf6bcfb51c7e90e76f6aa2f","tid":1297610,"uid":168267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:09:53.000Z","msg":"琴晚警犬失晒控咁亂咬人，記者都郁埋，喺鏡頭前面完全唔避忌<br />\n見到有人話佢哋放棄形象<br />\n話盧sir權力被架空<br />\n亦有人問，點解和理優最後都會拉人打人<br />\n<br />\n今日我哋就見到，依家人哋不單止唔驚，仲動作多多<br />\n不停先發制人去<span style=\"color: red;\">合理化琴晚嘅行動，方便日後繼續以過度武力打壓和平示威者</span><br />\n１。公共關係科總警司：議員用好多粗口挑釁警方<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1297082\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1297082</a><br />\n２。警犬發表聲明指出九點開始既MK係非法集結<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dfLzzT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dfLzzT</a><br />\n３。記協聲明失實 警方表遺憾<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dfKreT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dfKreT</a><br />\n４。警察隊員佐級協會去信梁君彥 指兩議員妨礙警察工作<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1297250\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1297250</a><br />\n<br />\n另外仲有的士司機從業員總會譴責琴晚嘅司機伯伯<br />\n同埋M記唔交CCTV<br />\n呢啲你話佢哋自己醒水奶共，警犬冇背後做嘢，我就打死都唔信喇<br />\n<br />\n雖然佢哋讀得書少，但唔可以鬆懈<br />\n冇腦嗰班，係好認同政府同警察永遠是對的<br />\n啱先我屋企睇有線，老母聽見泛民聯合聲明譴責琴晚警方暴力就冷笑咗聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇完呢啲９ｕｐ嘢，我哋成日笑完就算<br />\n但真係有批人會放咗喺心入便，慢慢會覺得差佬做嘢就係咁樣，而且依家人哋理直氣壯<br />\n<br />\n其實有咁多片、咁多證據，我哋可以做到啲咩去反擊？"},{"pid":"4c36d610ccbd37a49c859b8a9be10c0b2d9a9e56","tid":1297610,"uid":168267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:12:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />求解"},{"pid":"d5977007dc1d7beaffc7dc3968b928a3a3614903","tid":1297610,"uid":168267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:13:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />求解"},{"pid":"f2826dd6dd1583990a031dd78842476faac9603f","tid":1297610,"uid":65887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:15:52.000Z","msg":"前面嗰班就毅進仔啫<br />\n後面班軍司唔係呀<br />\n千祈唔好輕敵"},{"pid":"030b2a9e25c089dc0c213e4017740cf313e6e93a","tid":1297610,"uid":267337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:15:59.000Z","msg":"幫推正經post"},{"pid":"f27492472204f11940aac300e08651d05dfe490d","tid":1297610,"uid":127929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:16:31.000Z","msg":"[集思廣益]<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港警察，目中無人，敵視市民<br />\n香港警察，嚴人寬己，濫用暴力"},{"pid":"167b7f34be1b8ca15f68fbf4e9344baa1405f52a","tid":1297610,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:16:47.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">幫手推返啲緊要野上水\n今晚無任何活動 唔好比人玩到\n我代果班on9仔同各位義士手足道歉\n唔好比人玩到唔好嬲\n屌自己人都玩 下次無人出你地死撚緊\n唔好再有下次喇.....</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n幫手推下面啲POST<br />\n（急求）７７義士被控襲警求片！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1295985\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1295985</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n急！！！  我有個 旺角義士朋友 需要大家幫幫手拯救！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1295823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1295823</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n【突發】聽朝9點 屯門區議會 要人！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1297048\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1297048</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5a6df7f704c0911c2a9d7ad9a3b0327a51df5b25","tid":1297610,"uid":168267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:20:58.000Z","msg":"大家討論下<br />\n依家警犬擺明要聯合香港各界嚟打擊示威者<br />\n經過一晚，我哋以為警犬會失民心<br />\n結果多咗的士司機從業員總會同M記兩個盟友（aka香港人清算對象<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n明明證據喺晒我哋度，警犬都咁高調燒到去梁君彥嗰疊，有兩個可能<br />\n１。令民意偏向屌９泛民，抵銷晏晝泛民聯合聲明嘅效果<br />\n２。背後已經扯撚晒貓尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無論咩理由，以後佢哋要對議員郁手，都可以更輕易，更唔會引起民怨"},{"pid":"e35defa603750ca1e18b14f89882d32ccba159ce","tid":1297610,"uid":268106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:21:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"187bfb1fb3c88b2c72ec2a4aebd9c8bbe0e0aa2b","tid":1297610,"uid":168267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2826dd6dd1583990a031dd78842476faac9603f","tid":1297610,"uid":65887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:15:52.000Z","msg":"前面嗰班就毅進仔啫<br />\n後面班軍司唔係呀<br />\n千祈唔好輕敵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:22:23.000Z","msg":"exact7ly<br />\n革命尚未成功，咪撚鬆懈呀兒登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61818d24cbdc9a686e541cc057b7d402a0e93e7c","tid":1297610,"uid":168267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:23:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />求解"},{"pid":"1d05e7bb0b78bccd417fe75432ff5abd553e7ab1","tid":1297610,"uid":51023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:24:57.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"a44efae5f097eacb06c7c57aba7dfd17a0960173","tid":1297610,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:24:59.000Z","msg":"佢講大話既時候 我地係咪應該呼籲d受害者出黎？<br />\n當然要保障番佢地唔會比人秋後"},{"pid":"b67e6b2af15917209073c939f6b469dc77c23bbc","tid":1297610,"uid":168267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a44efae5f097eacb06c7c57aba7dfd17a0960173","tid":1297610,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:24:59.000Z","msg":"佢講大話既時候 我地係咪應該呼籲d受害者出黎？<br />\n當然要保障番佢地唔會比人秋後"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:27:15.000Z","msg":"要搵一個reach到大眾嘅平台<br />\n之前見過巴打話去組廣告板，覺得好好，唔知有冇下文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}